Tank circuit resonant frequency 
f r = 1 2 Ï€ L C
using variable capacitor with a constant inductor value will allow us to tune to specific frequencies
the only requirement for the inductor is that it allows the frequency response to go between the frequency values we specify, we want these to correspond with
AM radio station frequencies


